<h5 class="nx-font-semibold nx-tracking-tight nx-text-slate-900 dark:nx-text-slate-100 nx-mt-8 nx-text-lg">添加渲染通道（Pass）<a href="#添加渲染通道pass" id="添加渲染通道pass" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"></a></h5>
<p class="nx-mt-6 nx-leading-7 first:nx-mt-0">每个后处理效果都被称为一个 <strong>Pass</strong>，你可以将多个 Pass 添加到 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">EffectComposer</code> 中。常见的 Pass 包括 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">RenderPass</code> 和 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">OutlinePass</code>，它们分别用来渲染场景和实现描边效果。</p>
<p class="nx-mt-6 nx-leading-7 first:nx-mt-0">通过 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">composer.addPass()</code> 将不同的后处理效果添加到 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">EffectComposer</code> 中。</p>
